snippet.title: Savage young lioness - The big hunt (Windows game 1996)
snippet.description:
Savage young lioness is a TPS (third-person shooter) action game.

By the way, It has a very low resolution though It is a Windows 95 game.
Moreover, I don't know how to play well this game.
